BOX SIZING
Visible height = user defined + padding
---------------------------------------------
BORDER-BOX 
if you add 
box-sizing : border-box;
this will take height and width as it is wont add extra height of padding
Bcz of border-box visible size wont change
*PADDING AND BORDER WILL GET MINUS*
