display - flex;
will bring things in one line if they are in vertical line
(In this the images came side by side bcz of flexbox)


PROPERTIES OF FLEXBOX;
justify-content:space //manages space horizontally
align-items:center //will align items vertically

*IN ORDER TO CENTER 1 BOX U NEED TO USE FLEX AND THEN JUSTIFY AND ALIGN ITEMS 
Flexbox - it is used to perfectly center a div
